photo.title: Jugando al tenis sobre un aeroplano en pleno vuelo (Inglaterra, 192X)

description._content: My Website This was from a nice evening at Rodeo Beach back in February. I met up with my buddy Ed and we enjoyed an amazing sunset. I knew this spot had great potential after seeing so many nice sunset images from others. It was fun, after many attempts, to finally see the sky go off here in person.
